panels.name: List
text_labels: To access the dashboard, follow these steps:

Open the login page.
Enter your employee ID and password.
Click "Sign In".
If it's your first time logging in, you may be prompted to reset your password.
If you forget your password, click "Forgot Password?" to reset it.
After logging in, you’ll see the main dashboard, which includes:

✅ Quick Stats – View patient count, appointments, and system alerts. ✅ Navigation Menu – Access different sections like Patients, Appointments, Billing, and Reports. ✅ Recent Activities – Track updates and changes in real time. ✅ Search Bar – Quickly find patient records, invoices, or staff schedules.
